    "name": "Bat to the Beat",
    "steam_appid": 3236170,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swing your bat to the beat in this cricket-themed rhythm action game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Think on your feet</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a unique twist on rhythm gameplay that challenges your sense of rhythm and spatial awareness. At each beat you have to make a split second decision. Attack and risk getting caught by the fielders. Or defend and let the pressure build up. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemy positions and patterns are randomized to make each play-through unique, forcing you to think on your feet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236170/extras/e5207633f1be48566159f9e02bbf4347.poster.avif?t=1770818588\" width=800 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236170/extras/e5207633f1be48566159f9e02bbf4347.webm?t=1770818588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236170/extras/e5207633f1be48566159f9e02bbf4347.mp4?t=1770818588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Travel the world</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you make your way across the cricket-playing world you'll be challenged by the unique grooves of each country - ranging from  one-drop reggae beats of Jamaica to  syncopated Indian rhythms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236170/extras/920b4281fb0ff14945326a2aec9d0d75.poster.avif?t=1770818588\" width=800 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236170/extras/920b4281fb0ff14945326a2aec9d0d75.webm?t=1770818588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236170/extras/920b4281fb0ff14945326a2aec9d0d75.mp4?t=1770818588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight for the top spot</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you complete the campaign, you'll unlock the ability to compete on leaderboards for each level in the 'timeless test' mode. The longer you survive, the more frenetic the action gets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236170/extras/3e127fe2ed77dae10cfab76a6f0f3766.poster.avif?t=1770818588\" width=800 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236170/extras/3e127fe2ed77dae10cfab76a6f0f3766.webm?t=1770818588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236170/extras/3e127fe2ed77dae10cfab76a6f0f3766.mp4?t=1770818588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
